12 Gorgeous Real Wedding Moments That Will Lift Your Spirits Congratulations to all! üèÜ 
Hollywood stars hit the red carpet for the Oscars on Sunday dressed to the nines . But our readers who tied the knot this weekend gave those celebs a run for their money with their beautiful big day looks. 
See 12 gorgeous wedding moments below. 1 "It was 10 degrees out and rainy when we took this shot. The things we do for photographs!" -- Nikki 2 "Congrats to Heidi and Melissa who tied the knot in Sebring, Florida on this warm winter day!" -- Christophe Z. 3 "The day is here! Celebrating @joannakayla and Eugene's wedding." -- Lightedpixels Photography 4 ‚ÄúThis wedding was full of beautiful ladies that love and support each other. Tiffany and David Caesar are truly blessed to have friends that have turned into family." -- Anesha Collins 5 "Aida and Memso spend time together overlooking the Blue Ridge Mountains of North Carolina after their wedding yesterday at Hawkesdene." -- Hooman Bahrani 6 "Massachusetts couple Jane Peachy and Brian Kelley exchanged vows at the historic lighthouse in Vieques, Puerto Rico on Thursday." - - Sandy Malone of Sandy Malone Weddings and Events 7 "Jasmin and Jason tied the knot on Saturday afternoon at the Jupiter Gardens Event Center in Dallas, Texas." -- Tim and Lauren Johnson 8 "Mary Margaret and Sam Crews were married Feb. 25 in Columbia, South Carolina at their childhood church, St. John's Episcopal. These avid fly fishermen will be spending their honeymoon on the waters of Kiawah." -- Latoya Dixon 9 "The historical South Carolina State Museum, built in an old factory building, was the perfect spot for Tayler and Will's wedding this Saturday. Our favorite 'wow' location was the dome planetarium!" -- Katie Hart 10 "Ramona Alston and Michael Burkett were married on Feb. 25 at the Saluda Shoals River Center in Columbia, South Carolina." -- Purple Goose Photography 11 "Wedding of Thanh and Greg held in St. Francis Xavier Cathedral in Adelaide with reception held in the Mount Lofty House." -- Scott Goh 12 MIKE RICE PHOTOGRAPHY "Pat and Phil had a beautiful wedding at the Asheville Botanical Gardens." -- Mike Rice If you go to a wedding or get married yourself, hashtag your photos #HPrealweddings or e-mail one to us afterward and we may feature it on the site!
